# Tutorial tasks

Move a unit!\nClick on a unit > Click on a destination > Click the arrow popup = move a unit quickly!\nClick on a unti fast>Click on the destination>Click the arrow popup
Found a city!\nSelect the Settler (flag unit) > Click on 'Found city' (bottom-left corner) = make a city!\nSelecstx da settler boi(flag unti) >Clickona found cita(bottom left corner)
Enter the city screen!\nClick the city button twice = enter the citooo screeno!\nClick the city button twice
